Interface ToughkeyBase.ToughkeyCallback

public static interface ToughkeyBase.ToughkeyCallback extends android.os.Parcelable
Interface for Toughkey callbacks. Classes implementing this interface can handle events related to Toughkey detection, timeouts, and errors.
